<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html lang="en">

<Head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
    <title>Climate Solutions</title>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<div class="container mx-auto p-4">
  <div class="hero bg-base-100 rounded-lg mb-8">
    <div class="hero-content text-center">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Explore Our Climate Solutions</h1>
        <p class="py-6">
          Discover innovative projects that help fight climate change and protect our environment.
        </p>
        <a href="/solutions/projects" class="btn btn-primary">Explore Projects</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
    <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
      <figure>
        <img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/solution_biomass01.jpg" alt="Biomass Power" />
      </figure>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Biomass Power</h2>
        <p>Biomass feedstock can replace fossil fuels for generating heat and electricity. Perennial biomass offers a "bridge" to a clean, renewable energy future.</p>
        <div class="card-actions justify-end">
          <a href="/solutions/projects/4" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
      <figure>
        <img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/solution_farmlandirrigation01.jpg" alt="Farm Irrigation Efficiency" />
      </figure>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Farm Irrigation Efficiency</h2>
        <p>Drip and sprinkler irrigation, among other practices and technologies, make farm water use less energy/fuel intensive and conserve significant amounts of freshwater.</p>
        <div class="card-actions justify-end">
          <a href="/solutions/projects/5" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
      <figure>
        <img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/Solution_Bamboo01.jpg" alt="Bamboo Production" />
      </figure>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Bamboo Production</h2>
        <p>Bamboo rapidly sequesters carbon in biomass and soil and can thrive on degraded lands. Long-lived bamboo products can store carbon over time.</p>
        <div class="card-actions justify-end">
          <a href="/solutions/projects/6" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>